  </section>

  <!-- The house -->
  <section class="ed-section">
    <div class="ed-section-head"><h2>The house</h2></div>
    <div class="ed-prose">
      <p>An Airbnb Guest Favorite. Reviewers call out the well-stocked kitchen and comfortable beds. A paved walkway runs from the house down to the covered dock, so all ages can get to the water easily.</p>
    </div>
    <dl class="ed-kv" style="margin-top:18px;">
      <dt>Sleeping</dt><dd>6 king bedrooms (4 en suite on the main level) plus a kids' room with 2 bunk beds and a toddler bed. 10 beds across 7 bedrooms.</dd>
      <dt>Bathrooms</dt><dd>5.5</dd>
      <dt>Dock</dt><dd>Covered, deep-water, private boat slip. Swimmable, and you can fish right off it.</dd>
    </dl>
    <div class="ed-tags" style="margin-top:18px;">
      <span class="ed-tag">Full kitchen</span>
